creator: Cloudbooking
descriptionHtml:
This companion application is for bookers using the Cloudbooking services suite.

Whether it’s a room, desk or a parking space, CBMobile gives bookers greater on-the-go booking flexibility. With a sophisticated new user interface and improved user experience, CBMobile is stacked full of easy to use features, including:

* Automatic integration between Microsoft Outlook Exchange and Cloudbooking via the mobile app or browser, digital signage and Outlook calendars.

* Search across multiple locations, book, edit or cancel rooms, desks or parking spaces on the move.

* Logon – With both SSO & Non SSO.

This app is free to download, but a valid Cloudbooking license and logon ID is required to use this application.
